@startuml seq-14-cancel-order
' 序列图14：取消订单
title 取消订单序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "order.js" as Front
participant "ProductController" as Ctrl
participant "ProductService" as Svc
participant "ProductOrderMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击订单"取消"按钮
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/product/order/cancel(orderId)
Ctrl -> Svc: cancelOrder(orderId)
Svc -> Mapper: updateStatus(orderId, status=4 已取消)
Mapper -> DB: UPDATE product_order SET status=4 WHERE order_id=?
DB --> Mapper: 影响行数1
Mapper --> Svc: 成功
Svc --> Ctrl: 成功
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200}
Front -> Front: 从待支付列表移除
Front --> User: 提示订单已取消

@enduml
